high_descs: Turn and go to the table.
Pick up a knife on the table.
Turn and go to the counter by the microwave.
Cut a potato on the counter.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn and go to the counter by the microwave.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Put the slice of potato in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of potato in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the door and when you're a few steps away, head right to stand at the curved edge of the counter.
Pick up the sharp knife with a yellow handle from the counter.
Turn right and carry the knife to stand in front of the dishwasher.
Use the knife to slice the potato on the counter above the dishwasher.
Carry the knife to the microwave, which is to your left.
Place the knife on the blue plate inside the microwave.
Move right to stand back in front of the sliced potato.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Carry the potato to the microwave on your left.
Place the potato inside the microwave and then remove once heated.
Turn around and carry the potato towards the curved end of the counter, and then head left to the fridge.
Place the potato slice on the shelf next to the lettuce in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate a slice of hot potato.

high_descs: Turn left, go across the room, turn right and head to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right and head to the dishwasher.
Cut the potato on the counter.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the knife in the microwave and shut the microwave.
Turn right and go back to the counter above the dishwasher.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left and go back to the microwave.
Put the slice of potato in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Turn around, go to the counter, turn left and head to the fridge.
Put the slice of potato in the fridge to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in the fridge.
